ze:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">As marcas do passado amargam minha mente</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">De forma comovente fiz triste a can&ccedil;&atilde;o e a noite chorou</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Sozinho na noite feito um vagabundo e louco de amor</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Fa&ccedil;o das janelas meu palco de shows</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Me encolho, me humilho e canto o que sou:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Um caso perdido, um amante da lua</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Um incompreendido, um lixo da rua</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&Eacute; que sou poeta e poeta &eacute; louco</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Tem amor demais, tem de tudo um pouco</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Tem sede de justi&ccedil;a, esperan&ccedil;a no vento</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">E cr&ecirc; que em breve tempo o tempo de tristezas poder&aacute; findar</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Ari